WEBVTT

01:32.090 --> 01:34.890
[How dare you!?]

01:35.080 --> 01:37.910
[Episode 9]

01:38.979 --> 01:40.710
What Flower Festival Banquet?

01:41.170 --> 01:43.970
I think they're just bored
and want to waste money.

01:44.030 --> 01:46.229
Common people can barely afford to eat,

01:46.920 --> 01:49.520
yet they still have time
for such frivolities.

01:53.250 --> 01:54.610
This isn't the way back to the palace.

01:54.610 --> 01:56.830
I didn't dare call out to you
since you were walking this way

01:56.830 --> 01:57.960
with your head down.

01:57.970 --> 01:58.570
No wonder.

01:58.890 --> 02:00.090
-Let's—
-Consort Yu.

02:03.540 --> 02:04.770
The palace is so big,

02:05.640 --> 02:07.570
yet somehow I run into him everywhere.

02:07.570 --> 02:08.370
Such bad luck.

02:08.410 --> 02:09.270
Your Highness.

02:13.430 --> 02:14.090
Consort Yu.

02:14.940 --> 02:16.340
May I have a word with you?

02:18.200 --> 02:19.550
Wait for me over there.

02:20.170 --> 02:20.660
Yes.

02:25.570 --> 02:26.430
Your Highness,

02:26.880 --> 02:28.650
what brings you here?

02:30.520 --> 02:32.770
When I was young
and hadn't left the palace,

02:32.770 --> 02:34.210
if the servants beat me,

02:35.840 --> 02:37.410
I'd hide here

02:38.990 --> 02:40.650
and only return late at night.

02:41.550 --> 02:42.890
So now that I have time,

02:43.590 --> 02:45.590
I wanted to come back and take a look.

02:45.730 --> 02:46.530
Here it comes.

02:46.990 --> 02:48.780
The villain's monologue.

02:51.100 --> 02:51.730
Wanyin.

02:53.510 --> 02:54.510
Why do I feel that

02:56.590 --> 02:57.790
we've grown distant?

02:58.480 --> 02:59.320
It's not that.

03:00.180 --> 03:01.580
It's just that this place

03:01.870 --> 03:03.270
has too many prying eyes.

03:03.950 --> 03:06.150
My secret guards are watching the area.

03:06.610 --> 03:07.540
No one will come.

03:16.900 --> 03:18.700
Regarding what I said last time,

03:18.700 --> 03:20.210
have you thought about it?

03:20.960 --> 03:22.540
Can Your Highness foresee

03:23.420 --> 03:24.680
my decision too?

03:25.780 --> 03:26.780
What do you think?

03:27.720 --> 03:29.400
Dodging the question.

03:30.120 --> 03:32.290
Good thing I'm prepared.

03:35.270 --> 03:36.760
I panicked that day,

03:36.890 --> 03:37.930
and my words

03:38.770 --> 03:40.630
may have offended Your Highness.

03:41.530 --> 03:43.060
I embroidered this myself.

03:48.530 --> 03:49.320
Swallows

03:51.170 --> 03:52.170
flying together.

03:53.110 --> 03:55.310
It's "The Return of the Condor Heroes."

03:56.180 --> 03:57.880
You must've put some thought into this.

03:57.880 --> 03:59.740
As long as Your Highness likes it.

03:59.820 --> 04:01.940
Your Highness predicts things like a god,

04:01.940 --> 04:03.580
always making a move first.

04:05.060 --> 04:06.790
Could it be that you are also...

04:07.030 --> 04:07.830
Also what?

04:08.270 --> 04:09.620
One with foresight?

04:15.020 --> 04:15.450
Yes.

04:16.610 --> 04:17.529
I gained it

04:19.350 --> 04:19.870
quite recently.

04:19.870 --> 04:20.769
In your dreams,

04:21.600 --> 04:22.930
do you often see

04:22.930 --> 04:24.370
strange sights

04:25.270 --> 04:26.930
but don't know what they mean?

04:28.000 --> 04:29.120
They look...

04:31.150 --> 04:32.500
quite blurry.

04:32.840 --> 04:34.570
Dream interpretation is difficult.

04:34.570 --> 04:36.370
It's hard to explain it clearly.

04:36.970 --> 04:38.970
It is said those of the highest level

04:39.000 --> 04:41.480
can see all beings in the Six Realms.

04:41.730 --> 04:43.260
Just by closing their eyes,

04:43.520 --> 04:45.450
they can reveal heaven's secrets.

04:45.600 --> 04:47.820
But everyone is different,

04:48.409 --> 04:49.800
so what they see

04:50.210 --> 04:51.180
varies.

04:51.730 --> 04:52.510
Makes sense.

04:53.220 --> 04:55.250
Since Your Highness is a prince,

04:55.870 --> 04:57.340
can you see more?

04:57.890 --> 04:59.550
Things further in the future?

05:00.100 --> 05:01.960
A few days ago, I foresaw in a dream

05:02.030 --> 05:03.910
that an expert appeared
beside His Majesty.

05:03.910 --> 05:05.430
He took you out of the palace in disguise

05:05.430 --> 05:06.400
to a lake

05:06.740 --> 05:08.370
to speak with some commoners.

05:08.370 --> 05:10.570
I was merely worried about your safety,

05:11.870 --> 05:13.870
so I sent men to follow you secretly.

05:14.740 --> 05:17.340
But unexpectedly,
this expert acted without any warning

05:17.340 --> 05:19.340
and killed many of my secret guards.

05:20.120 --> 05:22.450
With such a dangerous person by your side,

05:22.490 --> 05:24.150
how can I be at ease?

05:25.460 --> 05:26.760
He beat around the bush

05:26.990 --> 05:28.520
just to get things out of me.

05:28.990 --> 05:30.450
I'd never seen this person

05:30.580 --> 05:31.910
in the palace either.

05:32.700 --> 05:34.430
I was truly terrified that day.

05:34.580 --> 05:36.909
What about after returning to the palace?

05:37.380 --> 05:38.380
Have you seen him?

05:39.980 --> 05:40.780
No, I haven't.

05:41.930 --> 05:42.700
Is that so?

05:45.120 --> 05:45.980
Your Highness,

05:46.890 --> 05:48.090
do you not believe me?

05:52.280 --> 05:53.080
Of course not.

05:54.280 --> 05:56.170
I wonder if you could use your foresight

05:56.170 --> 05:57.030
to divine for me

05:58.030 --> 05:59.030
where this person

05:59.960 --> 06:01.480
is right now.

06:02.510 --> 06:04.010
Doesn't Your Highness know

06:04.010 --> 06:05.320
that the scenes in the dreams

06:05.320 --> 06:06.260
are bizarre

06:06.690 --> 06:08.620
and bestowed by the will of Heaven.

06:08.840 --> 06:10.440
It is not something we can dream

06:10.440 --> 06:11.770
just because we want to.

06:16.240 --> 06:17.780
Perhaps, just for my sake,

06:19.590 --> 06:20.360
give it a try,

06:21.200 --> 06:21.880
will you?

06:35.250 --> 06:35.909
Insidious.

06:36.570 --> 06:37.100
Cunning.

06:37.270 --> 06:39.070
-My Lady, wait for me!
-Thick-skinned too!

06:39.070 --> 06:40.110
My Lady!

06:40.060 --> 06:41.950
[Zhaoyang Hall]

06:42.460 --> 06:43.460
I'm so pissed off.

06:48.070 --> 06:50.330
It's exhausting every time I talk to him.

06:50.710 --> 06:52.900
What does Xie Yong'er see in him anyway?

06:52.900 --> 06:55.300
He flirts everywhere and plays both sides.

06:56.100 --> 06:59.700
Quite fitting of his name Duan
which means to balance both sides.

07:02.630 --> 07:03.490
Your Highness,

07:04.070 --> 07:05.830
Dan has something very important

07:05.830 --> 07:06.510
for you.

07:07.730 --> 07:08.340
What?

07:12.420 --> 07:15.080
Dan asked me to watch you
practice calligraphy.

07:17.210 --> 07:18.060
Calligraphy?

07:19.080 --> 07:21.140
I did want to practice brush writing,

07:21.380 --> 07:23.710
but I have other things
to think about now.

07:23.890 --> 07:24.690
I have no time.

07:25.070 --> 07:26.660
You can always make time.

07:25.910 --> 07:27.480
[Yong]

07:29.890 --> 07:30.780
Besides,

07:30.900 --> 07:32.000
Dan said Your Highness

07:32.000 --> 07:34.030
only needs to practice
the character "Yong" well,

07:34.030 --> 07:35.960
and you'll master all characters.

07:36.290 --> 07:37.890
He wrote this for you personally.

07:37.690 --> 07:40.700
[Yong]

07:38.409 --> 07:40.340
Don't let his kindness go to waste.

07:43.220 --> 07:45.020
It looks pretty decent.

07:45.570 --> 07:47.070
When did he practice this behind my back?

07:47.070 --> 07:48.659
Just practice, Your Highness.

07:48.659 --> 07:49.990
I'll stay here with you.

07:50.020 --> 07:51.150
I won't go anywhere.

07:59.900 --> 08:00.780
Yong.

08:05.830 --> 08:06.510
Yong.

08:07.510 --> 08:08.220
Yong.

08:08.780 --> 08:10.330
The "Yong" in Xie Yong'er.

08:13.950 --> 08:14.420
Yong.

08:15.270 --> 08:15.660
Crap.

08:16.270 --> 08:17.930
I fell for Prince Duan's trap.

08:17.980 --> 08:19.220
All that nonsense I spouted—

08:19.220 --> 08:21.020
he definitely didn't buy it all.

08:21.780 --> 08:23.240
With his cautious nature,

08:23.540 --> 08:26.070
he might go check with
Xie Yong'er right away.

08:26.340 --> 08:29.270
If Xie Yong'er doesn't say
she gained the foresight,

08:29.390 --> 08:30.990
and our stories don't match,

08:31.190 --> 08:32.169
then I'm doomed.

08:32.980 --> 08:33.630
Mr. Bei.

08:34.570 --> 08:35.350
Tell me,

08:35.770 --> 08:37.830
how can you make someone keep a secret

08:37.890 --> 08:39.150
and not tell anyone else?

08:39.150 --> 08:41.150
How is your relationship with them?

08:41.289 --> 08:42.140
Not good.

08:42.750 --> 08:43.610
Whatever I say,

08:43.940 --> 08:45.420
she won't believe a single word.

08:45.420 --> 08:46.080
Lock her up.

08:46.180 --> 08:47.010
That won't work.

08:47.010 --> 08:48.180
I can't lock her up forever.

08:48.180 --> 08:49.180
Then silence her.

08:49.220 --> 08:50.160
That's even worse.

08:50.160 --> 08:51.100
She has to stay alive.

08:51.100 --> 08:52.100
Then I don't know.

08:52.780 --> 08:53.910
Nothing works.

08:54.230 --> 08:55.220
What should I do?

09:00.110 --> 09:00.970
Your Highness.

09:02.150 --> 09:02.570
You...

09:04.660 --> 09:07.790
[Yong]

09:05.440 --> 09:06.120
Oh shoot.

09:06.940 --> 09:08.260
What the hell did I write?

09:08.260 --> 09:09.780
Your handwriting, Your Highness,

09:09.780 --> 09:11.350
is like wandering dragons
and painted phoenixes.

09:11.350 --> 09:12.880
If you take it to the market,

09:13.150 --> 09:14.880
it could ward off evil spirits.

09:17.050 --> 09:19.050
Thanks for the compliment, Mr. Bei.

09:22.660 --> 09:24.060
Ward off evil spirits...

09:24.710 --> 09:25.200
I got it!

09:27.020 --> 09:28.590
Prince Duan is definitely a 2D character.

09:28.590 --> 09:31.590
He suspects you, me,
and Xie Yong'er are the same kind.

09:31.700 --> 09:33.470
I lied that the three of us
gained the foresight,

09:33.470 --> 09:34.730
and fooled him for now.

09:35.470 --> 09:37.900
But just in case Xie Yong'er's story
doesn't match ours,

09:37.900 --> 09:39.340
we need to stage a supernatural event

09:39.340 --> 09:40.300
to scare her.

09:41.220 --> 09:43.630
Anyway, we can't let Prince Duan
trick her into talking.

09:43.630 --> 09:45.320
CEO Dan, I'll leave it to you.

09:46.640 --> 09:47.900
As expected of Wanyin.

09:50.630 --> 09:52.390
Noble Consort Yu's handwriting...

09:52.390 --> 09:54.070
Dan, you can actually read it?

09:56.460 --> 09:57.000
Mr. Bei.

09:57.900 --> 09:59.360
I might have to trouble you

09:59.590 --> 10:00.990
in the time that follows.

10:07.940 --> 10:08.830
Crown Prince.

10:09.640 --> 10:13.420
[15 years ago]

10:10.150 --> 10:10.660
Dot.

10:11.630 --> 10:12.360
Horizontal.

10:12.630 --> 10:13.230
Vertical.

10:13.590 --> 10:13.940
Rise.

10:14.940 --> 10:18.490
[Young Xiahou Dan]

10:15.030 --> 10:15.910
Left-falling.

10:16.630 --> 10:17.560
Right-falling.

10:19.590 --> 10:21.720
Master writing the character "Yong,"

10:21.820 --> 10:22.750
and you can write

10:22.840 --> 10:24.190
all other characters well.

10:24.190 --> 10:24.920
Practice it.

10:26.050 --> 10:29.340
[Yong]

10:37.870 --> 10:39.230
Isn't this book called

10:39.230 --> 10:41.870
"Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort."

10:41.870 --> 10:43.590
There's gotta be a transmigrated heroine

10:43.590 --> 10:45.540
with a protagonist plot, right?

10:46.540 --> 10:48.270
Where on earth is she?

10:52.910 --> 10:55.130
[Yong]

11:03.670 --> 11:06.090
[Yong]

11:09.430 --> 11:10.070
Eunuch An.

11:10.890 --> 11:11.980
It is so late.

11:12.400 --> 11:14.530
Why did His Majesty suddenly summon me

11:14.530 --> 11:16.200
with so many Imperial Guards?

11:16.500 --> 11:17.630
Is something wrong?

11:18.680 --> 11:19.540
Your Highness,

11:19.780 --> 11:21.770
I am not sure about that.

11:22.110 --> 11:24.040
But ever since you attended to him,

11:24.300 --> 11:26.630
His Majesty has been lost in thought alone

11:27.180 --> 11:28.370
and always

11:28.870 --> 11:30.270
muttering something...

11:30.770 --> 11:32.510
"Those not on my side,

11:32.950 --> 11:34.100
they must..."

11:35.370 --> 11:36.670
"They must..."

11:36.960 --> 11:38.910
They must be disloyal?

11:39.390 --> 11:40.710
Yes, that is it.

11:40.900 --> 11:42.300
"They must be disloyal."

11:42.470 --> 11:44.330
There is another line after that.

11:46.680 --> 11:47.640
What is it?

11:49.370 --> 11:50.810
"Execute them!"

11:55.500 --> 11:56.900
Let's go, Your Highness.

12:18.910 --> 12:19.770
Your Highness,

12:20.200 --> 12:21.130
go inside quickly.

12:21.130 --> 12:22.860
His Majesty is waiting for you.

13:11.420 --> 13:13.320
Those not on my side,

13:14.180 --> 13:16.300
they must be disloyal.

13:17.060 --> 13:18.680
Execute them!

13:29.060 --> 13:29.700
My dear,

13:30.480 --> 13:32.810
I have been waiting for you
for a long time.

13:34.030 --> 13:34.830
Your Majesty,

13:35.570 --> 13:37.470
what's going on here?

13:38.270 --> 13:39.970
What is a platform?

13:41.200 --> 13:42.610
What is an idol?

13:43.240 --> 13:44.450
What is the plot?

13:44.470 --> 13:45.730
What is a 2D character?

13:49.360 --> 13:50.160
Your Majesty,

13:51.600 --> 13:53.800
I don't know what you are talking about.

13:59.460 --> 14:01.980
The things you told me when you were drunk

14:02.310 --> 14:03.710
were truly interesting.

14:08.700 --> 14:10.040
Who exactly are you?

14:10.640 --> 14:12.030
Why do you always know things

14:12.030 --> 14:13.510
that are unheard of?

14:17.110 --> 14:18.020
I am...

14:19.270 --> 14:19.820
I...

14:20.180 --> 14:21.310
Perhaps Consort Xie

14:21.410 --> 14:23.000
has gained the foresight

14:23.610 --> 14:25.380
and can foresee the future.

14:25.510 --> 14:26.170
Foresight?

14:26.560 --> 14:27.360
That's right.

14:27.640 --> 14:29.090
Those with roots of wisdom

14:29.090 --> 14:31.490
can predict the future using

14:32.030 --> 14:33.950
drunkenness or dreams.

14:35.210 --> 14:36.270
Is that so?

14:42.520 --> 14:43.320
Your Majesty,

14:45.420 --> 14:45.780
I...

14:45.940 --> 14:47.410
I-I do...

14:48.790 --> 14:50.790
I do know a little about divination.

14:56.650 --> 14:58.310
Why didn't you say so earlier?

15:00.420 --> 15:00.780
Come.

15:00.970 --> 15:01.770
Rise, my dear.

15:09.920 --> 15:11.050
These past few days,

15:11.670 --> 15:14.250
your drunken ramblings

15:15.680 --> 15:17.780
really scared me to death.

15:18.760 --> 15:20.520
So it was all a misunderstanding.

15:20.520 --> 15:21.850
Do not blame me, my dear.

15:25.410 --> 15:26.190
After all,

15:29.260 --> 15:31.400
No one wants their bedfellow

15:34.640 --> 15:35.930
to be on the other side.

16:08.510 --> 16:09.370
Your Highness?

16:10.180 --> 16:10.800
Yong'er.

16:18.680 --> 16:20.080
It's so late in the night—

16:21.320 --> 16:22.580
why are you here alone?

16:25.550 --> 16:26.690
Your Highness,

16:27.420 --> 16:29.590
His Majesty is busy
with official business,

16:29.590 --> 16:30.940
s-so I...

16:32.160 --> 16:33.420
did not stay the night,

16:33.500 --> 16:35.450
and wanted to take a walk.

16:36.770 --> 16:37.720
Why are you here?

16:38.060 --> 16:39.390
His Majesty summoned me

16:39.940 --> 16:41.070
to discuss matters.

16:43.990 --> 16:45.120
What a coincidence.

16:54.280 --> 16:55.880
Ever since the library fire,

16:56.720 --> 16:59.230
it has been inconvenient for me
to come to the harem.

16:59.230 --> 17:00.380
Seeing you

17:01.820 --> 17:04.079
is harder than ascending to the heavens.

17:04.950 --> 17:05.760
Yes.

17:06.900 --> 17:09.230
We haven't seen each other
for a long time.

17:10.700 --> 17:11.849
Then why did you

17:12.700 --> 17:14.250
not write to me?

17:15.660 --> 17:17.500
His Majesty and the Empress Dowager

17:17.500 --> 17:18.900
have people watching me.

17:20.180 --> 17:21.680
No matter how selfish I am,

17:25.940 --> 17:27.339
how could I put my beloved

17:28.220 --> 17:29.070
in danger?

17:33.440 --> 17:34.440
Your Highness...

17:36.070 --> 17:37.470
I have one more question.

17:38.260 --> 17:39.500
The silk pouch you gave me,

17:39.500 --> 17:41.100
contained a brilliant plan.

17:41.220 --> 17:42.550
It was truly ingenious.

17:43.500 --> 17:45.300
But you stay in the harem all day,

17:46.170 --> 17:48.300
and have no contact with those people.

17:49.150 --> 17:50.560
How did you know

17:51.590 --> 17:53.090
about these secrets?

17:54.440 --> 17:55.850
I...

17:56.870 --> 17:59.110
no one wants their bedfellow

18:02.180 --> 18:03.590
to be on the other side.

18:04.660 --> 18:05.260
What is it?

18:07.790 --> 18:08.500
I

18:09.900 --> 18:11.360
know a little divination.

18:12.260 --> 18:13.970
I often see things about the future

18:13.970 --> 18:15.350
in my dreams.

18:16.590 --> 18:17.920
Something like that...

18:19.980 --> 18:20.840
Your Highness,

18:21.480 --> 18:23.210
you can understand it this way.

18:23.930 --> 18:25.390
I'm the kind of person
described in storybooks

18:25.390 --> 18:26.590
who knows divination

18:26.690 --> 18:29.130
and gains foresight through dreams.

18:30.110 --> 18:32.510
Otherwise, how could I foresee the future?

18:38.130 --> 18:39.940
It's just that when these dreams come

18:39.940 --> 18:41.150
and whether they are accurate

18:41.150 --> 18:42.080
depend entirely

18:42.790 --> 18:44.350
on heaven's will.

18:44.740 --> 18:45.740
That is why I never

18:45.740 --> 18:47.200
told you the truth before.

18:47.220 --> 18:49.150
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

18:50.590 --> 18:51.370
Your Highness,

18:51.370 --> 18:52.430
someone is coming.

19:02.030 --> 19:02.760
Don't worry.

19:04.420 --> 19:05.960
I will keep your secret.

19:19.790 --> 19:21.200
Did Xie Yong'er really say that

19:21.200 --> 19:21.860
last night?

19:22.980 --> 19:23.790
Word for word.

19:26.150 --> 19:27.210
Thank you, Mr. Bei,

19:27.260 --> 19:28.720
for eavesdropping for me.

19:29.830 --> 19:31.620
Anything for you.

19:33.490 --> 19:34.160
How is she?

19:34.820 --> 19:36.670
She was scared out of her wits.

19:37.980 --> 19:38.790
I mean Wanyin.

19:39.420 --> 19:39.980
Her?

19:40.480 --> 19:42.480
She laughed so hard.

19:43.540 --> 19:46.330
You actually summoned Prince Duan
to the palace on purpose

19:46.330 --> 19:48.260
to create opportunities for them.

19:49.190 --> 19:49.980
CEO Dan!

19:50.450 --> 19:51.880
You're terrible!

19:52.390 --> 19:53.970
I've settled the scholars.

19:54.310 --> 19:56.170
When can we get rid of Xie Yong'er?

19:56.700 --> 19:58.260
I make her drunk every day.

19:58.700 --> 19:59.960
I can't drink anymore.

20:02.070 --> 20:03.270
Wine is food essence.

20:03.480 --> 20:05.550
The more you drink, the younger you get.

20:05.550 --> 20:07.700
You have a beauty in your arms,
yet you're unhappy?

20:07.700 --> 20:08.430
Keep acting.

20:11.680 --> 20:13.130
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

20:12.030 --> 20:14.630
It's just two ellipsis—
need I run all the way there?

20:13.210 --> 20:14.830
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

20:15.150 --> 20:15.590
Then,

20:15.240 --> 20:16.460
♪ Incredible ♪

20:16.510 --> 20:17.670
I can add a few more ellipsis?

20:16.950 --> 20:17.980
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

20:18.580 --> 20:19.460
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

20:18.630 --> 20:19.930
Don't rush.

20:19.620 --> 20:21.280
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

20:20.260 --> 20:22.130
Xie Yong'er
hasn't done anything wrong yet.

20:21.620 --> 20:22.760
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

20:22.390 --> 20:23.840
You can't just turn on her, can you?

20:23.190 --> 20:24.510
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

20:24.310 --> 20:24.840
Besides,

20:24.860 --> 20:27.710
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

20:25.350 --> 20:27.950
Prince Duan is wavering back and forth
between Xie Yong'er and me.

20:27.950 --> 20:29.540
♪ From day to night ♪

20:28.500 --> 20:29.900
We can't just push Xie Yong'er

20:29.680 --> 20:31.110
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

20:29.980 --> 20:31.180
towards Prince Duan.

20:31.200 --> 20:32.750
♪ From the present to the past ♪

20:32.870 --> 20:34.000
♪ It's always you ♪

20:34.490 --> 20:35.990
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

20:34.830 --> 20:36.590
If Xie Yong'er falls out with Prince Duan,

20:36.010 --> 20:37.550
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

20:36.730 --> 20:37.830
do I have to be responsible for her?

20:37.620 --> 20:40.500
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

20:38.950 --> 20:40.580
She is the female lead.

20:40.740 --> 20:41.920
She will have plenty of help.

20:40.830 --> 20:43.930
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

20:42.460 --> 20:44.090
You should worry about yourself first.

20:43.980 --> 20:45.880
♪ With you ♪

20:46.480 --> 20:48.760
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

20:46.510 --> 20:47.310
Wait, Mr. Bei.

20:48.350 --> 20:49.430
I missed an exclamation mark.

20:48.820 --> 20:50.400
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

20:50.440 --> 20:52.400
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

20:52.890 --> 20:55.180
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

20:53.310 --> 20:54.240
What did she say?

20:55.230 --> 20:56.740
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

20:56.760 --> 20:58.780
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

20:59.650 --> 21:01.250
Are you telling me what to do?

21:04.440 --> 21:05.600
That is right.

21:05.990 --> 21:08.280
Haven't I always been
telling you what to do?

21:08.280 --> 21:08.770
Mr. Bei.

21:09.250 --> 21:10.750
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

21:09.610 --> 21:10.070
[That is right.]

21:10.090 --> 21:10.530
[Haven't I always been
telling you what to do?]

21:10.600 --> 21:12.690
How long are you two
going to talk like this?

21:10.840 --> 21:12.500
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

21:13.000 --> 21:13.780
I am just

21:14.640 --> 21:16.050
helping Wanyin practice writing.

21:16.050 --> 21:16.660
Look.

21:17.600 --> 21:19.080
[That is right.]

21:18.140 --> 21:19.110
Hasn't her handwriting

21:19.110 --> 21:20.630
[Haven't I always been
telling you what to do?]

21:19.480 --> 21:20.800
improved?

21:24.720 --> 21:26.610
Come hit me if you dare.

21:25.690 --> 21:26.910
♪ Incredible ♪

21:27.290 --> 21:28.470
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

21:28.890 --> 21:29.920
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

21:29.520 --> 21:30.970
You aren't practicing calligraphy at all.

21:30.000 --> 21:31.780
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

21:31.700 --> 21:32.490
I think

21:32.110 --> 21:33.130
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

21:32.750 --> 21:34.630
you are just wasting my internal force.

21:33.660 --> 21:34.890
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

21:35.380 --> 21:38.100
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

21:37.340 --> 21:38.440
Thank you for your trouble, Mr. Bei.

21:38.440 --> 21:40.020
♪ From day to night ♪

21:39.140 --> 21:39.740
By the way,

21:40.120 --> 21:41.630
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

21:40.290 --> 21:41.690
two scholars are coming later.

21:41.690 --> 21:43.240
♪ From the present to the past ♪

21:42.220 --> 21:43.030
Wanyin

21:43.100 --> 21:44.820
might need to work remotely with everyone.

21:43.310 --> 21:44.420
♪ It's always you ♪

21:44.970 --> 21:46.400
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

21:45.790 --> 21:46.390
No, I mean—

21:46.470 --> 21:47.980
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

21:46.930 --> 21:48.900
she might need to communicate
via handwritten notes.

21:48.090 --> 21:50.940
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

21:49.850 --> 21:50.690
So...

21:51.150 --> 21:52.320
I have to trouble you, Mr. Bei,

21:51.330 --> 21:54.290
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

21:52.680 --> 21:54.080
to run a few more errands.

21:54.350 --> 21:56.300
♪ With you ♪

21:55.550 --> 21:55.900
Here.

21:56.150 --> 21:57.650
Talk face to face.

21:56.850 --> 21:59.210
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

21:58.550 --> 21:59.190
Talk.

21:59.330 --> 22:00.830
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

22:00.900 --> 22:02.800
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

22:01.360 --> 22:03.340
Your Majesty, why did you summon me?

22:03.340 --> 22:05.600
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

22:03.790 --> 22:05.320
It's not appropriate for us

22:05.630 --> 22:07.110
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

22:05.980 --> 22:07.200
to meet right now, is it?

22:07.200 --> 22:09.210
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

22:08.630 --> 22:10.350
It's because Li Yunxi and Cen Jintian

22:10.350 --> 22:11.550
are coming over soon.

22:12.390 --> 22:15.650
How great is this?
You should've talked like this long ago.

22:19.590 --> 22:21.120
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

22:21.300 --> 22:22.900
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

22:22.070 --> 22:22.810
Actually,

22:23.550 --> 22:26.210
Li Yunxi and Cen Jintian
are coming over in a bit.

22:26.220 --> 22:27.720
You can meet them.

22:28.460 --> 22:29.990
I forged identities for them,

22:29.990 --> 22:31.450
and gave them a sum of money

22:31.620 --> 22:33.110
for them to buy official titles.

22:33.110 --> 22:34.300
They've managed to get

22:34.300 --> 22:36.050
minor positions in various ministries.

22:36.050 --> 22:37.250
In the past,

22:37.530 --> 22:39.800
if scholars heard
about getting office this way,

22:39.800 --> 22:41.380
they would have turned up their noses

22:41.380 --> 22:42.510
and spat in disgust.

22:43.180 --> 22:45.290
But after the incident at the lake...

22:46.100 --> 22:47.760
It seems they've all grown up.

23:01.790 --> 23:03.250
Greetings, Your Majesty.

23:03.550 --> 23:04.010
At ease.

23:04.070 --> 23:05.470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

23:12.420 --> 23:13.700
How inappropriate!

23:15.310 --> 23:17.510
I humbly request Her Highness to leave.

23:19.350 --> 23:19.960
Leave?

23:21.870 --> 23:22.740
On the boat that day,

23:22.740 --> 23:24.900
Her Highness's presence
was already overstepping.

23:24.900 --> 23:26.940
Today you've even entered
the Imperial Study.

23:26.940 --> 23:28.310
The harem interfering in politics

23:28.310 --> 23:29.270
is absolutely inappropriate.

23:29.270 --> 23:29.830
Enough!

23:30.390 --> 23:31.190
Your Majesty,

23:34.590 --> 23:35.250
I am willing

23:35.420 --> 23:37.600
to advise you even at the cost of my life.

23:37.600 --> 23:39.990
They haven't grown up at all.

23:42.870 --> 23:43.830
What should we do?

23:43.830 --> 23:44.390
Watch me.

23:55.740 --> 23:58.270
Mr. Li,
after falling into the water that day,

23:58.630 --> 23:59.890
how are your injuries?

24:00.550 --> 24:01.310
Are you

24:02.030 --> 24:03.230
fully recovered now?

24:06.830 --> 24:07.180
Come!

24:07.560 --> 24:08.560
Give me your hand!

24:10.550 --> 24:11.480
I've recovered.

24:13.070 --> 24:14.820
Mr. Li, please calm down first.

24:15.590 --> 24:17.450
It's not too late to advise later.

24:22.550 --> 24:23.490
This hand of mine

24:25.010 --> 24:26.340
is practically ruined.

24:36.220 --> 24:38.150
That's Best Actress level acting.

24:44.830 --> 24:45.350
Mr. Li,

24:46.410 --> 24:47.670
have a cup of tea first.

24:50.650 --> 24:51.480
I will...

24:52.740 --> 24:53.890
take my leave now.

24:54.630 --> 24:55.170
Wanyin!

25:04.570 --> 25:06.570
You work tirelessly
for the country

25:06.740 --> 25:08.110
and the people.

25:09.850 --> 25:11.550
I see them all.

25:13.600 --> 25:14.460
But some people

25:15.800 --> 25:18.800
are so full of prejudice
that they can't tolerate you.

25:21.460 --> 25:23.190
Even I feel ashamed for them.

25:23.550 --> 25:25.030
I am just a woman after all.

25:27.360 --> 25:28.580
In this country,

25:30.510 --> 25:32.220
there may be no place for me.

25:33.700 --> 25:35.630
Great righteousness and kindness

25:36.890 --> 25:38.390
have nothing to do with me.

25:38.980 --> 25:39.840
Your Highness,

25:39.980 --> 25:40.390
I...

25:40.420 --> 25:42.630
If it weren't for Your Highness that day,

25:42.630 --> 25:44.090
we wouldn't be here today.

25:48.500 --> 25:49.460
Your Highness is noble.

25:49.460 --> 25:51.780
I am willing to atone with my death.

25:55.900 --> 25:56.550
Done.

25:56.790 --> 25:57.660
Easy.

25:59.550 --> 26:00.750
He even knelt for you.

26:01.070 --> 26:02.850
Piece of cake.

26:12.260 --> 26:12.790
Lord Jia.

26:14.660 --> 26:15.520
Your Highness.

26:15.550 --> 26:17.590
General Luo had someone send back a horse

26:17.590 --> 26:18.560
and a letter.

26:24.890 --> 26:28.620
[For Prince Duan to receive personally]

26:35.220 --> 26:36.110
In this life,

26:36.500 --> 26:37.630
I have few fortunes.

26:38.220 --> 26:39.590
Fighting on the battlefield

26:39.590 --> 26:41.310
to serve the country is one.

26:42.130 --> 26:43.400
Meeting His Highness

26:43.700 --> 26:46.560
and fighting the Yan rebels together
is the second.

26:46.870 --> 26:49.070
Whenever I recall
our three years of bitter war—

26:49.070 --> 26:50.590
how there was no distinction
between ruler and subject,

26:50.590 --> 26:52.100
only the bond of comrades—

26:52.500 --> 26:54.100
I find it even more precious.

26:54.980 --> 26:57.290
I return His Highness's warhorse

26:57.420 --> 26:58.880
as a token of my sincerity.

26:59.400 --> 27:01.400
I, Luo Changsheng, kneel in thanks.

27:08.670 --> 27:11.630
General Luo
is truly a man of deep loyalty.

27:13.340 --> 27:14.850
He is reminding me

27:16.150 --> 27:17.750
not to forget to save his son.

27:19.760 --> 27:21.640
First, the Minister of Revenue,

27:21.760 --> 27:23.280
and now, Grand Tutor Wei.

27:23.790 --> 27:24.900
The Empress Dowager

27:24.900 --> 27:27.150
blames us for all this.

27:27.360 --> 27:29.580
She won't let it go easily.

27:29.890 --> 27:31.710
But by forcing my hand like this,

27:32.480 --> 27:34.540
even with our deep bonds and history,

27:35.040 --> 27:36.370
it is difficult to do it.

27:37.600 --> 27:38.190
But...

27:38.800 --> 27:40.380
if we do nothing,

27:40.680 --> 27:42.800
General Luo might turn against us.

27:43.530 --> 27:45.840
The Empress Dowager has Luo Yi too.

27:46.010 --> 27:47.870
That puts us at a disadvantage.

27:48.180 --> 27:49.180
Usually,

27:49.290 --> 27:52.550
the Empress Dowager uses Luo Yi
to keep General Luo in line.

27:52.570 --> 27:54.120
But in a crisis,

27:54.660 --> 27:57.330
he could become a weapon used against us.

27:58.880 --> 28:00.270
So we have to do this.

28:02.760 --> 28:04.360
Send a message to Mr. Murong.

28:04.730 --> 28:06.190
Ask him if he has any ideas.

28:06.980 --> 28:07.700
That way,

28:08.700 --> 28:10.700
we can distract the Empress Dowager

28:11.410 --> 28:13.120
so she won't trouble Luo Yi.

28:14.500 --> 28:16.030
It will also show General Luo

28:16.030 --> 28:17.750
that we are doing our part.

28:18.110 --> 28:18.570
Yes.

28:26.350 --> 28:27.210
Your Highness.

28:27.520 --> 28:28.380
Your Highness.

28:28.430 --> 28:29.170
T-Then...

28:29.820 --> 28:31.080
What about this horse?

28:32.720 --> 28:33.580
You can have it.

28:34.750 --> 28:36.210
Thank you, Your Highness.

28:39.110 --> 28:40.700
Military officials
returning to the capital to report

28:40.700 --> 28:42.560
must not stay longer than 15 days.

28:42.700 --> 28:45.740
General Luo didn't leave
until the morning of the 16th day.

28:45.740 --> 28:47.700
This can be either a minor or major issue.

28:46.970 --> 28:50.520
[Chen Danian,
Chen Dasui's brother]

28:48.070 --> 28:50.080
I can find an excuse

28:50.240 --> 28:52.370
to charge him with perverting the law.

28:54.030 --> 28:56.940
Don't we have his son?

28:57.150 --> 28:59.250
Instead of convicting him,

28:59.900 --> 29:03.230
why not find a way
to make him useful to us?

29:04.980 --> 29:06.300
Lord Chen,

29:06.350 --> 29:09.750
don't just talk.

29:10.070 --> 29:11.700
Don't be like your brother.

29:11.730 --> 29:13.220
Use your brain.

29:13.580 --> 29:14.330
Yes.

29:16.550 --> 29:17.550
Empress Dowager,

29:17.710 --> 29:20.240
I have finished confiscating
the Wei estate.

29:20.580 --> 29:21.380
We seized

29:21.630 --> 29:24.110
15 property deeds
and 20,000 taels of gold.

29:26.500 --> 29:27.760
Here is the inventory.

29:30.970 --> 29:33.730
Grand Tutor Wei
was convicted by the Emperor.

29:34.360 --> 29:35.400
Let him handle it.

29:36.110 --> 29:38.710
His Majesty is unfamiliar
with state affairs.

29:38.980 --> 29:41.500
Matters of the court, big or small,

29:41.690 --> 29:44.260
still require your decision,
Your Majesty.

29:49.700 --> 29:51.710
Which should go to the treasury,

29:51.940 --> 29:53.630
and which should not—

29:54.830 --> 29:56.760
it is your decision, Your Majesty.

30:10.480 --> 30:11.510
[Great Xia Agriculture]

30:11.590 --> 30:15.510
[Sweet Potato]

30:15.590 --> 30:18.660
[Great Xia Agriculture]

30:26.550 --> 30:27.750
How long have you been

30:28.310 --> 30:29.640
recording in this book?

30:30.830 --> 30:32.070
About 10 years.

30:33.360 --> 30:34.350
For these 10 years,

30:34.350 --> 30:35.830
I have maintained across Great Xia

30:35.830 --> 30:38.070
a small experimental field in each region.

30:38.070 --> 30:40.440
It was to study the climate, soil,

30:40.630 --> 30:43.460
planting times, irrigation methods,
and other factors' impact

30:43.460 --> 30:44.610
on the harvest.

30:45.420 --> 30:46.790
I now have a system on

30:46.830 --> 30:48.730
what to plant and how to plant

30:49.030 --> 30:50.220
in which area.

30:51.010 --> 30:51.540
Lord Cen,

30:52.450 --> 30:53.700
do the crops listed

30:54.120 --> 30:55.350
include Yan millet?

30:55.870 --> 30:56.590
Yan millet?

30:58.110 --> 30:59.120
It should be...

30:59.740 --> 31:01.340
just some sporadic records.

31:01.870 --> 31:04.110
It is not common in Great Xia.

31:04.470 --> 31:06.500
What about other drought-resistant crops?

31:06.500 --> 31:08.190
Why do you ask, Your Highness?

31:19.390 --> 31:21.150
The Imperial Astronomer reports

31:21.150 --> 31:22.980
an anomaly in the celestial phenomena.

31:22.980 --> 31:24.180
In the next two years,

31:24.830 --> 31:26.560
there will be a severe drought.

31:31.740 --> 31:32.820
This matter

31:33.690 --> 31:34.500
is top secret.

31:38.450 --> 31:39.010
I

31:39.350 --> 31:40.630
will not leak a word.

31:43.800 --> 31:45.130
It hasn't happened yet.

31:45.790 --> 31:46.790
If we prepare now,

31:47.060 --> 31:48.180
when the time comes,

31:48.180 --> 31:49.240
no one will starve.

31:51.500 --> 31:52.300
Official Cen?

31:54.110 --> 31:56.760
Although Yan millet tastes poor,

31:56.940 --> 31:58.700
it ripens two to three times a year.

31:58.700 --> 32:00.270
If planted widely,

32:01.030 --> 32:03.490
it could indeed
save lives during a drought.

32:04.920 --> 32:05.710
Great Xia

32:06.270 --> 32:08.530
has no tradition of planting Yan millet.

32:08.790 --> 32:10.230
To start planting now,

32:10.310 --> 32:12.240
we must first convince the people.

32:12.500 --> 32:13.550
As for Yan millet seeds,

32:13.550 --> 32:14.750
perhaps the court can

32:14.870 --> 32:16.530
purchase them from Yan State.

32:17.900 --> 32:19.160
The treasury is empty.

32:20.590 --> 32:21.850
The court has no money.

32:30.980 --> 32:33.900
And there is much friction on the border
between Yan State and Great Xia.

32:33.900 --> 32:34.700
And now,

32:35.390 --> 32:37.830
the military power
is entirely in Prince Duan's hands,

32:37.830 --> 32:39.830
and the national treasury is empty.

32:40.620 --> 32:42.280
Neither soft nor hard tactics

32:42.350 --> 32:43.610
can be implemented.

32:45.420 --> 32:47.270
But I must introduce Yan millet

32:47.940 --> 32:49.800
to save the people from disaster.

32:50.750 --> 32:51.350
That is why

32:52.740 --> 32:54.270
I have gathered you all here

32:54.390 --> 32:55.650
to discuss a solution.

32:57.150 --> 32:58.110
I have an idea.

32:58.790 --> 33:00.720
We might not need to spend any money

33:00.830 --> 33:01.690
to obtain

33:02.110 --> 33:04.040
a large amount of Yan millet seeds.

33:05.680 --> 33:07.080
Can you be more specific?

33:11.070 --> 33:12.400
We shall take our leave.

33:28.980 --> 33:29.780
What's wrong?

33:35.520 --> 33:37.050
Is your head hurting again?

33:37.700 --> 33:38.410
A little.

33:49.040 --> 33:50.250
These ministers

33:50.630 --> 33:52.290
are actually quite reliable.

33:53.850 --> 33:55.180
Let's follow their plan

33:55.310 --> 33:56.240
step by step.

33:56.730 --> 33:57.790
Maybe we really can

33:58.180 --> 33:59.380
prevent the drought.

34:00.280 --> 34:00.900
Yes.

34:02.400 --> 34:03.330
You finally have

34:03.630 --> 34:05.290
right-hand men,

34:06.040 --> 34:07.500
no longer fighting alone.

34:08.199 --> 34:10.130
But you don't sound happy about it.

34:14.739 --> 34:17.670
Are we being too optimistic?

34:19.730 --> 34:20.790
What if Prince Duan

34:21.530 --> 34:23.659
and the Empress Dowager get in our way?

34:24.420 --> 34:25.210
Or what if

34:26.460 --> 34:27.639
they get suspicious

34:28.040 --> 34:29.699
and discover our entire plan?

34:30.030 --> 34:31.860
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

34:31.860 --> 34:32.659
Leave it to me.

34:40.489 --> 34:42.620
So you've already thought it through.

34:47.590 --> 34:48.070
Wanyin.

34:49.110 --> 34:49.639
Sit down.

35:02.780 --> 35:03.840
There's something

35:04.510 --> 35:06.910
I've been wanting
to ask you for a long time.

35:07.970 --> 35:09.700
Who do you think leaked the news

35:09.730 --> 35:12.280
of our meeting
with the scholars on the lake

35:13.700 --> 35:15.300
to Prince Duan?

35:19.330 --> 35:21.260
I haven't figured that out either.

35:21.740 --> 35:22.800
You think it was me,

35:24.180 --> 35:24.680
right?

35:27.040 --> 35:29.300
You think I leaked the news
to Prince Duan,

35:29.300 --> 35:31.300
then put on a show for the scholars,

35:32.340 --> 35:33.480
going so far as to

35:33.860 --> 35:35.160
sacrifice a life

35:35.910 --> 35:37.570
just to win their trust.

35:41.810 --> 35:42.420
Oh, right.

35:43.070 --> 35:44.400
The fire in the library—

35:44.860 --> 35:46.410
do you also think I did it?

35:47.150 --> 35:48.820
After all, judging by the outcome,

35:48.820 --> 35:50.480
Xu Yao was backed into a corner

35:51.030 --> 35:52.890
and indeed handed over that book.

35:54.340 --> 35:55.740
And all these incidents,

35:56.590 --> 35:58.250
the one who benefited the most

35:58.470 --> 35:58.990
was me.

36:00.940 --> 36:02.340
It's not because of that.

36:09.220 --> 36:10.000
Then why?

36:14.710 --> 36:15.870
That day on the boat,

36:16.520 --> 36:19.120
we talked to the scholars
for four whole hours.

36:20.220 --> 36:21.730
Today in the Imperial Study,

36:21.730 --> 36:23.590
we talked for another four hours.

36:24.360 --> 36:25.500
You said a lot

36:25.890 --> 36:27.750
and showed off a lot of knowledge,

36:28.440 --> 36:29.690
but your knowledge of economics

